@DietAI.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5001
@ContentType = application/json

### Auth Endpoints

### Login User
POST {{DietAI.Api_HostAddress}}/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password"
}

###

### Plan Endpoints

### Send Plan Request
POST {{DietAI.Api_HostAddress}}/v1/plan/send
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}
X-User-Id: user123

{
  "description": "Diet plan request",
  "preferences": []
}

###

### Send Plan Update
POST {{DietAI.Api_HostAddress}}/v1/plan/update
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}
X-User-Id: user123

{
  "planId": "plan123",
  "updates": []
}

###
